## The Outcome

We were able to launch the website on time with improvements to the original design. We’re all hoping that getting the College’s website to this milestone will encourage leadership to fund content strategy and a full redesign in the future. But in the meantime, TSCT has a functional, search-optimized website ready to serve its future students.
